 {
  coords 7043.334 107.094 5124.009
  m_sTitle "Situation"
  m_sTextData "U.S. Special Forces have been reported in the area to the South of OBJ PizzaDox. USSR Spetnaz have been dispatched to defend vital intelligence from falling into the hand of American forces. The Americans are already on there way. Defences are already in place."\
  ""\
