 {
  coords 7061.236 110.608 4893.037
  m_sTitle "Execution"
  m_sTextData "Drive to OBJ PizzaDox"\
  "Defend"\
  "Do not let the enemy secure the intel"\
  ""\
  "The intel is randomly placed on the OBJ inside a structure. You should try to locate it so that way you can keep tabs on it. It could be hidden extremely well."\
  ""\
  "You shall not pickup or move the intel. If you accidentaly pick it up, drop it in the house."
